citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:00AM on 21-
February-2023.
The inspector arrived at the facility and knocked on the door. The inspector talked to a family member whom stated no
one was available for an inspection today. The inspector then left the facility.
End Section
